Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:13.59,zhushi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(168,88)}平擊球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:13.59,zhushi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(172,134)}削球
